t follow, Pia must confront her own shame and fear, risking everything to see justice--and love--triumph at last.--cPublisher's description. 0aInfluenza Epidemic, 1918-1919vFiction. 0aImmigrantsvFiction. 0aOrphansvFiction. 0aOrphanagesvFiction. 0aJusticevFiction. 7aHistorical fiction.2lcgft 7aBildungsromans.2lcgft 0aLarge type books.  c(OCoLC)1201681161  c4659d4659